pr_title: added feature to share/copy story link
pr_body:
fixes: #23 

Feature added to share on social media platforms or copy the link of the story page.  I have added two options. One is to share on social media and other is to copy the URL of page.
I have taken example of eos-icons.com for LinkedIn, facebook and whatsapp template example.
